---
---
<section class="social-proof py-5 position-relative z-1" style="background-color: transparent;">
  <div class="container py-4 reveal">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-lg-5 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
        <h2 class="display-5 text-dark mb-3" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">Por Qué Este Curso<br><span class="text-accent" style="font-style: italic;">Es Diferente</span></h2>
        <div style="width: 40px; height: 1px; background-color: #d97706;" class="mb-4"></div>
        <p class="text-muted fs-5 fw-light lh-lg">Este no es un curso para aprender a meditar. Es un sistema para dejar de vivir en piloto automático, incluso cuando la vida no se detiene.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-7">
        <div class="row g-4 text-center">
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <div class="light-panel p-4 h-100 border-accent-subtle bg-white shadow-sm">
              <span class="d-block display-3 text-dark mb-2" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">7</span>
              <strong class="d-block fs-6 text-accent text-uppercase tracking-wide">Módulos</strong>
              <span class="text-muted small font-italic">de transformación</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <div class="light-panel p-4 h-100 border-accent-subtle bg-white shadow-sm">
              <span class="d-block display-3 text-dark mb-2" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">14</span>
              <strong class="d-block fs-6 text-accent text-uppercase tracking-wide">Manuales</strong>
              <span class="text-muted small font-italic">aplicación real</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <div class="light-panel p-4 h-100 border-accent-subtle bg-white shadow-sm">
              <span class="d-block display-3 text-dark mb-2" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">29</span>
              <strong class="d-block fs-6 text-accent text-uppercase tracking-wide">Audios</strong>
              <span class="text-muted small font-italic">meditaciones guiadas</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  @import '../styles/variables.scss';
  
  .border-accent-subtle {
    border-top: 2px solid rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.4) !important;
  }
</style>
